            <div class="btoArticleTitle">Ai o maşină cu o vechime de maxim 8 ani?</div>
            <div class="btoArticleText">
                <div class="btoArticleAbstract">
                    <p>Dealerul tău Ford te poate ajuta să o schimbi cu una nouă.<br>Indiferent de marcă, mașinile cu vechime de p&acirc;nă la 8 ani se pot schimba, la Ford, cu unul dintre modelele Fiesta, B-MAX, C-MAX, Kuga, Focus&nbsp;sau Mondeo.* <br><br>Mașina nu este pe numele tău? Nu e o problemă &ndash; &icirc;n acest program sunt acceptate și vehiculele aflate in proprietatea unei rude de gradul I a potenţialului client. <br><br>Vino la cel mai apropiat dealer Ford, iar consultanții noștri &icirc;ți vor evalua mașina. Suplimentar faţă de evaluare, vei primi un extra bonus din partea Ford. <br><br>Pentru detalii despre oferta specială, poţi descărca de aici listele detaliate de preţuri:</p><ul><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri Ford Fiesta - Trade In (67,1 KB)" HREF="/cs/BlobServer?blobtable=MungoBlobs&amp;blobcol=urldata&amp;blobheadervalue1=attachment%3Bfilename%3D%22Lista+de+preturi+Ford+Fiesta+-+Trade+In.pdf%22&amp;blobheadervalue2=abinary%3Bcharset%3DUTF-8&amp;blobheadername1=Content-Disposition&amp;blobheadername2=MDT-Type&amp;blobheader=application%2Fpdf&amp;blobwhere=1214489546466&amp;blobkey=id" CLASS="download" onClick="if (typeof sford == 'object') omnitureLinkDownloadClick('brand:pdf download:retail price list','','','','','pdf download','',false,'ford fiesta','2013','car');" >Oferta specială Trade In &ndash; Ford Fiesta</a></li><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri Ford B-MAX - Trade In (65,3 KB)" HREF="/cs/BlobServer?blobtable=MungoBlobs&amp;blobcol=urldata&amp;blobheadervalue1=attachment%3Bfilename%3D%22Lista+de+preturi+Ford+B-MAX+-+Trade+In.pdf%22&amp;blobheadervalue2=abinary%3Bcharset%3DUTF-8&amp;blobheadername1=Content-Disposition&amp;blobheadername2=MDT-Type&amp;blobheader=application%2Fpdf&amp;blobwhere=1214489407627&amp;blobkey=id" CLASS="download" onClick="if (typeof sford == 'object') omnitureLinkDownloadClick('brand:pdf download:retail price list','','','','','pdf download','',false,'ford b-max','2012','car');" >Oferta specială Trade In &ndash; Ford B-MAX</a></li><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri Ford C-MAX - Trade In (66,1 KB)" HREF="/cs/BlobServer?blobtable=MungoBlobs&amp;blobcol=urldata&amp;blobheadervalue1=attachment%3Bfilename%3D%22Lista+de+preturi+Ford+C-MAX+-+Trade+In.pdf%22&amp;blobheadervalue2=abinary%3Bcharset%3DUTF-8&amp;blobheadername1=Content-Disposition&amp;blobheadername2=MDT-Type&amp;blobheader=application%2Fpdf&amp;blobwhere=1214489407667&amp;blobkey=id" CLASS="download" onClick="if (typeof sford == 'object') omnitureLinkDownloadClick('brand:pdf download:retail price list','','','','','pdf download','',false,'ford c-max','2011','car');" >Oferta specială Trade In -- Ford C-MAX</a></li><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri Ford Kuga - Trade In (67,2 KB)" HREF="/cs/BlobServer?blobtable=MungoBlobs&amp;blobcol=urldata&amp;blobheadervalue1=attachment%3Bfilename%3D%22Lista+de+preturi+Ford+Kuga+-+Trade+In.pdf%22&amp;blobheadervalue2=abinary%3Bcharset%3DUTF-8&amp;blobheadername1=Content-Disposition&amp;blobheadername2=MDT-Type&amp;blobheader=application%2Fpdf&amp;blobwhere=1214489407647&amp;blobkey=id" CLASS="download" onClick="if (typeof sford == 'object') omnitureLinkDownloadClick('brand:pdf download:retail price list','','','','','pdf download','',false,'ford kuga','2013','car');" >Oferta specială Trade In - Ford Kuga</a></li><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri Ford Focus - Trade In (66 KB)" HREF="/cs/BlobServer?blobtable=MungoBlobs&amp;blobcol=urldata&amp;blobheadervalue1=attachment%3Bfilename%3D%22Lista+de+preturi+Ford+Focus+-+Trade+In.pdf%22&amp;blobheadervalue2=abinary%3Bcharset%3DUTF-8&amp;blobheadername1=Content-Disposition&amp;blobheadername2=MDT-Type&amp;blobheader=application%2Fpdf&amp;blobwhere=1214489407727&amp;blobkey=id" CLASS="download" onClick="if (typeof sford == 'object') omnitureLinkDownloadClick('brand:pdf download:retail price list','','','','','pdf download','',false,'ford focus','2015','car');" >Oferta specială Trade In - Ford Focus</a></li><li><a TITLE="Listă de prețuri noul Ford Mondeo -